{"tid":2493984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美日峯會｜日報章頭版全是台灣　政治學者：從未見過","createTime":"2021-04-18T10:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T10:56:39.000Z","uid":271829,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ee88b2a0dd26655fb41c1a396ca437c517a7ece9","tid":2493984,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YieD4IJ9rr8_N2T_9ydSeCF7Kgc=/535x300/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L3TJSFS2RFFJNINHPU6YBT7OEI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYieD4IJ9rr8_N2T_9ydSeCF7Kgc%3D%2F535x300%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL3TJSFS2RFFJNINHPU6YBT7OEI.jpg&h=7f8e6046&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本各大報章均以美日峯會聯合聲明提及台灣作頭版報道。日本學者小笠原欣幸表示，從未見過。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n小笠原欣幸在貼文附上一張日本4份報紙頭版照片，包括《讀賣新聞》、《產經新聞》、《朝日新聞》及《每日新聞》，均以頭版頭條報道美日聯合聲明中提及台灣。<br />\n小笠原欣幸寫道：「今天日本報紙的頭條都是「台灣」！不只是頭版，裏面大幅度報道都圍繞台灣，我個人沒看過台灣佔這麼大的版面，顯現日美共同聲明包含台灣的重要性。」<br />\n<br />\n拜登與菅義偉舉行峯會後發表聯合聲明，就台灣、釣魚台、香港、新疆及南海等問題表達關切，當中特別強調台灣海峽和平與安定重要性同時，推動和平解決兩岸問題。這是繼1969年時任日本首相佐藤榮作與美國總統尼克遜（Richard Nixon）會面以來，日美再度在領袖會談聯合聲明中載明台灣，同時也是從1972年日本與中國建交以來的首度。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210418/5JP6EHFLEZH7FLIPTNOI47JKGE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210418%2F5JP6EHFLEZH7FLIPTNOI47JKGE%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RE9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=b5a2978d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210418%2F5JP6EHFLEZH7FLIPTNOI47JKGE%2F&h=60250437\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210418/5JP6EHFLEZH7FLIPTNOI47JKGE/</a>"},{"pid":"5b6e1b7427680ae7b04fd697d4b4e973d6108d5c","tid":2493984,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:18:17.000Z","msg":"珍珠聯盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec0dc40d58243bd9abc14dbd148c143c9083141","tid":2493984,"uid":8308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:23:08.000Z","msg":"台灣有美日盟友乜都夠了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e719535006137d6234d3051eb9c5ba020997409","tid":2493984,"uid":66202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:24:26.000Z","msg":"Taiwan No. 1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df67af81970c6008ce4909fc9ebdcdfa5d652b55","tid":2493984,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:26:56.000Z","msg":"陰謀論啲講,幾多個幼女都唔會賣到台灣<br />\n<br />\n支那霸曬啲資源後,所謂deep state都開唔到飯"},{"pid":"0c29da995cf081a0ab859ad98030e599fb1df816","tid":2493984,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:27:18.000Z","msg":"台灣者係日本條頸，落入中共手上者係比人勒住，覺醒得太慢啦"},{"pid":"22393a30afadf3809ff05facb2d57c5449df71dd","tid":2493984,"uid":276865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df67af81970c6008ce4909fc9ebdcdfa5d652b55","tid":2493984,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:26:56.000Z","msg":"陰謀論啲講,幾多個幼女都唔會賣到台灣<br />\n<br />\n支那霸曬啲資源後,所謂deep state都開唔到飯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:30:09.000Z","msg":"食台灣幼女"},{"pid":"6a19fd1321325814fbbd410b61481671d6dbfe2c","tid":2493984,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22393a30afadf3809ff05facb2d57c5449df71dd","tid":2493984,"uid":276865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df67af81970c6008ce4909fc9ebdcdfa5d652b55","tid":2493984,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:26:56.000Z","msg":"陰謀論啲講,幾多個幼女都唔會賣到台灣<br />\n<br />\n支那霸曬啲資源後,所謂deep state都開唔到飯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:30:09.000Z","msg":"食台灣幼女"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:32:19.000Z","msg":"高質個大頭雌激素嬰兒"},{"pid":"719220a9d012e097935a22f110ef6876ae4